 in a different band that it transmits?" %>      <%= form_text_field form, :keeper, label: "Keeper's call sign",                          help_text: "Whoever maintains and/or runs this repeater." %>      <%= form_textarea_field form, :notes, help_text: "This will be in the public record of the repeater." %>      <%= form_text_field form, :web_site %>      <%= form_multi_boolean_field form,                                   label: "What modes are supported by this repeater?",                                   fields: [{ name: :fm },                                            { name: :m17 },                                            { name: :dstar },                                            { name: :fusion },                                            { name: :dmr },                                            { name: :nxdn },                                            { name: :p25 },                                            { name: :tetra },                                            { name: :echolink }] %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3">    <div>      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7">FM</h2>      <p class="mt-1  text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Only applicable if the repeater supports FM.</p>    </div>    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 md:col-span-2">      <%= form_select_field form, :fm_ctcss_tone,                            choices: Repeater::CTCSS_TONES,                            options: { include_blank: "None" },                            help_text: "The CTCSS or access tone for this repeater, if it uses one. " %>      <%= form_boolean_field form, :fm_tone_burst, label: "Tone burst?",                             second_label: "Yes, this repeater uses tone burst." %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3">    <div>      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7">M17</h2>      <p class="mt-1  text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Only applicable if the repeater supports M17.</p>    </div>    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 md:col-span-2">      <%= form_select_field form, :m17_can,                            choices: Repeater::M17_CANS,                            options: { include_blank: "None" } %>      <%= form_text_field form, :m17_reflector_name %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3">    <div>      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7">D-Star</h2>      <p class="mt-1  text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Only applicable if the repeater supports D-Star.</p>    </div>    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 md:col-span-2">      <%= form_text_field form, :dstar_port %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3">    <div>      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7">Fusion</h2>      <p class="mt-1  text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Only applicable if the repeater supports Fusion.</p>    </div>    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 md:col-span-2">      <%= form_text_field form, :wires_x_node_id %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3">    <div>      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7">DMR</h2>      <p class="mt-1  text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Only applicable if the repeater supports DMR.</p>    </div>    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 md:col-span-2">      <%= form_select_field form, :dmr_color_code,                            choices: Repeater::DMR_COLOR_CODES,                            options: { include_blank: "None" } %>      <%= form_text_field form, :dmr_network, help_text: "Likely something like BRANDMEISTER or freeDMR, but there are many others." %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3">    <div>      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7">EchoLink</h2>      <p class="mt-1  text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Only applicable if the repeater supports EchoLink.</p>    </div>    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 md:col-span-2">      <%= form_text_field form, :echolink_node_number %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3">    <div>      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7">Location</h2>      <p class="mt-1  text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Without the location, the repeater will be impossible        to find.</p>    </div>    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 md:col-span-2">      <%= form_text_field form, :input_address, help_text: "Address where the repeater is. You can leave it blank and still have the rest of the fields here." %>      <%= form_text_field form, :input_locality %>      <%= form_text_field form, :input_region, help_text: "Or any other region demarcation" %>      <%= form_text_field form, :input_post_code %>      <%= form_select_field form, :input_country_id,                            choices: Country.order(:name).map { |c| [c.name, c.id] },                            options: { include_blank: "Please, choose a country" } %>      <%= form_text_field form, :input_latitude, help_text: "If blank, we'll figure it out from the address or grid square." %>      <%= form_text_field form, :input_longitude, help_text: "If blank, we'll figure it out from the address or grid square." %>      <%= form_text_field form, :input_grid_square, help_text: "If blank, we'll calculate it from the latitude and longitude." %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3">    <div>      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-7">Other</h2>      <p class="mt-1  text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Nice-to-haves, if you know them.</p>    </div>    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 md:col-span-2">      <%= form_text_field form, :tx_antenna, help_text: "Model or any details about the transmit antenna." %>      <%= form_select_field form, :tx_antenna_polarization, choices: %w[vertical horizontal], options: { include_blank: "Unknown" } %>      <%= form_text_field form, :tx_power, label: "Transmit power", help_text: "Expressed in watts." %>      <%= form_text_field form, :rx_antenna, label: "Receive antenna", help_text: "Model or any details about the receive antenna." %>      <%= form_select_field form, :rx_antenna_polarization, choices: %w[vertical horizontal], options: { include_blank: "Unknown" } %>      <%= form_text_field form, :bearing %>      <%= form_text_field form, :altitude_agl, help_text: "This is expressed in meters. If you have it in feet, multiply by 0.3048." %>      <%= form_text_field form, :altitude_asl, help_text: "This is expressed in meters. If you have it in feet, multiply by 0.3048." %>      <%= form_text_field form, :channel, help_text: "In some countries, the frequencies are divided in channels. Here you can enter the channel information." %>    </div>  </div>  <div class="pt-5">    <div class="flex justify-end">      <button type="submit" class="button">        <% if repeater.new_record? %>          <i class="fa-solid fa-plus mr-2"></i>          Add Repeater        <% else %>          <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square mr-2"></i>          Update Repeater        <% end %>      </button>    </div>  </div><% end %>